#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc51
msgctxt "sn35.121:51.1"
msgid "“Evaṃ passaṃ, rāhula, sutavā ariyasāvako cakkhusmimpi nibbindati, rūpesupi nibbindati, cakkhuviññāṇepi nibbindati, cakkhusamphassepi nibbindati, yampidaṃ cakkhusamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedanāgataṃ saññāgataṃ saṅkhāragataṃ viññāṇagataṃ tasmimpi nibbindati … pe … "
msgstr "“Seeing this, a learned noble disciple grows disillusioned with the eye, sights, eye consciousness, and eye contact. And they become disillusioned with anything included in feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness that arises conditioned by eye contact. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.121:51.2"
msgid "jivhāyapi nibbindati, rasesupi nibbindati, jivhāviññāṇepi nibbindati, jivhāsamphassepi nibbindati, yampidaṃ jivhāsamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedanāgataṃ saññāgataṃ saṅkhāragataṃ viññāṇagataṃ tasmimpi nibbindati … pe …. "
msgstr "They grow disillusioned with the ear … nose … tongue … body … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc52
msgctxt "sn35.121:52.1"
msgid "Manasmimpi nibbindati, dhammesupi nibbindati, manoviññāṇepi nibbindati, manosamphassepi nibbindati, yampidaṃ manosamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedanāgataṃ saññāgataṃ saṅkhāragataṃ viññāṇagataṃ tasmimpi nibbindati. "
msgstr "They grow disillusioned with the mind, thoughts, mind consciousness, and mind contact. And they grow disillusioned with anything included in feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness that arises conditioned by mind contact. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.121:52.2"
msgid "Nibbindaṃ virajjati; virāgā vimuccati; vimuttasmiṃ vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "Being disillusioned, desire fades away. When desire fades away they’re freed. When they’re freed, they know they’re freed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.121:52.3"
msgid "‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti pajānātī”ti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any state of existence.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc53
msgctxt "sn35.121:53.1"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā. "
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. "

msgctxt "sn35.121:53.2"
msgid "Attamano āyasmā rāhulo bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandi. "
msgstr "Satisfied, Venerable Rāhula was happy with what the Buddha said. "

msgctxt "sn35.121:53.3"
msgid "Imasmiñca pana veyyākaraṇasmiṃ bhaññamāne āyasmato rāhulassa anupādāya āsavehi cittaṃ vimucci. "
msgstr "And while this discourse was being spoken, Rāhula’s mind was freed from defilements by not grasping. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.121:53.4"
msgid "Anekānañca devatāsahassānaṃ virajaṃ vītamalaṃ dhammacakkhuṃ udapādi: "
msgstr "And the stainless, immaculate vision of the Dhamma arose in those thousands of deities: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.121:53.5"
msgid "“yaṃ kiñci samudayadhammaṃ sabbaṃ taṃ nirodhadhamman”ti. "
msgstr "“Everything that has a beginning has an end.” "

